Reasoning: The paper discusses a grant-free multiple access system that requires activity detection, channel estimation, and data decoding in one shot, which are all related to information theory (cs.IT). The system is designed for massive machine type communication (MTC) scenario, which involves network infrastructure (cs.NI) and signal processing (cs.SI). The paper also proposes a Multiple Measurement Model (MMV) model based massive MIMO, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM).
